Remove unused parameter
Add venv and Makefile for development
Add configuration for universal wheel
Move TestSuite.to_xml_string and TestSuite.to_file to functions that are not part of the TestSuite class. Add deprecation warnings for old interface
Use black to format the code. Use flake8-black plugin to test black violations
Do not throw Exception exceptions. Use TypeError that is more specific
Be more specific in flake8 rules that are ignored for specific parts of the code
Exclude tests package for setuptools. Remove test_suite from setuptools configuration. Better to just run the tests using tox and pytest than through setuptools
Delete MANIFEST.in file. It does not add anything to setuptools
Move tests and helpers to tests package
Convert tests to pytest style. Separate suite and case test modules. Break out test helpers. Fix flake8 issues. Fix formatting.
Fix pytest warnings for test module (#52)

Tox travis python support (#53)

* Drop support for py26, py32, py33, and py34. Add support for py35, py36, py37.

* Use shallow clone in travis
